member.summary:
Adds the  to the request pipeline.


Call this after UseAuthentication() and before UseAuthorization():


app.UseRouting();
app.UseAuthentication();
app.UseMultiTenantAuth();
app.UseAuthorization();
app.MapControllers();

member.remarks:
Recommended pipeline order:

app.UseRouting();
app.UseAuthentication();
app.UseMultiTenantAuth();   // ← here
app.UseAuthorization();
app.MapControllers();
